<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
<style>/* ===== TECHNOLOGY INTRO STYLES ===== */
.technology-hero {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00695c, #26a69a);
  padding: 80px 20px;
  text-align: center;
  color: #ffffff;
}

.technology-hero h1 {
  font-size: 3rem;
  margin-bottom: 15px;
}

.technology-tagline {
  font-size: 1.2rem;
  color: #b2dfdb;
  max-width: 700px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.technology-intro {
  padding: 60px 20px;
  background-color: #f0fdf9;
}

.technology-intro-container {
  max-width: 900px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  text-align: center;
}

.technology-intro-container h2 {
  font-size: 2.2rem;
  color: #00695c;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.technology-intro-container p {
  font-size: 1.05rem;
  line-height: 1.7;
  color: #333;
}

/* Responsive adjustments */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .technology-hero h1 {
    font-size: 2.3rem;
  }

  .technology-tagline {
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .technology-intro-container h2 {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
  }

  .technology-intro-container p {
    font-size: 1rem;
  }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
   <!-- views/partials/technology-intro.ejs -->
<section class="technology-hero">
  <div class="technology-hero-content">
    <h1>Our Technology</h1>
    <p class="technology-tagline">
      Leveraging smart tools and AI to improve crop productivity and optimize farming.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="technology-intro">
  <div class="technology-intro-container">
    <h2>Why Technology Matters in Farming</h2>
    <p>
      At Digital Krishi, we integrate modern technology into agriculture to help farmers
      increase crop yield, reduce losses, and make informed decisions. Our tools include
      IoT-based soil monitoring, AI-driven crop recommendations, precision irrigation, 
      and predictive weather analysis. By embracing technology, farmers can achieve 
      sustainable growth and secure better livelihoods, especially in rural areas.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
 
</body>
</html>